      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It's always a good idea to prioritize your work commitments, but do be cautious with the wound care. Antibiotic ointment and a warm compress can be helpful, but make sure to use a gentle compress and avoid applying too much pressure. You can also consider using a product like Neosporin or Bacitracin, which has anti-inflammatory properties. Just be sure to follow the instructions on the packaging and don't overdo it with the ointment or compresses.",
      "source": "target",
